# Package Manager Rules
- Always use yarn as the package manager
- NEVER add the "packageManager" field to any package.json files
- The packageManager field should only be present in nomlog-app/package.json (for EAS compatibility)
- When editing package.json files, only modify the specific fields requested, do not add packageManager

# API Specific Rules
- For nomlog-api: Do not add packageManager field to package.json
- For nomlog-app: The packageManager field is already present and should not be modified

# Agent Rules
- Always state agent model and version used in summary of changes